
---

### 2. .gitignore
Save this as `.gitignore`. This prevents unnecessary system files from being uploaded to Git.

```text
# Logs
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*

# OS generated files
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db

# IDE specific files
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~